have\ndefault cases. Additionally, tasks are created simply with the given\narguments, since error handling has been done beforehand. Moreover,\nindex-based commands such as mark, unmark and delete run through\nTaskList, which simply takes in the index.\n\nAdding assertions to these methods will ensure that future changes to\nthe codebase will not result in runtime errors.\n\nLet\u0027s,\n* add assertions to the switch cases, to ensure all cases have been\n  covered\n* add assertions to Task and subclass constructors to avoid invalid\n  objects being created\n* add assertions to TaskList methods to avoid causing runtime errors\n  from retrieving tasks from an invalid index\n","tags":["A-FullCommitMessage"],"fileTypesAndContributionMap":{"java":{"insertions":19,"deletions":1}}},{"hash":"a4f256bbd3cdf542cb84d718156ffd948b2a946d","isMergeCommit":false,"messageTitle":"Shifting CommandWord to package bmo.command","messageBody":"In the current codebase, the CommandWord enum is stored in the\nbmo.parser package. This seems counter-intuitive, especially since\nCommandWord is a property of Command.\n\nPeople looking at the codebase for the first time will struggle to find\nthe CommandWord enum.\n\nLet\u0027s shift the CommandWord enum to the bmo.command package for a\ncleaner distribution of class files.\n","fileTypesAndContributionMap":{"java":{"insertions":17,"deletions":19}}},{"hash":"c37e04b5d2ac1ba83e7e86ac319f36dbe1bc5f03","isMergeCommit":false,"messageTitle":"Shift Ui\u0027s role from printer to response formatter","messageBody":"Currently, Ui\u0027s task of printing has been taken over by the GUI provided\nby JavaFX. This means that messages printed out via the command-line do\nnot have a use anymore.\n\nHowever, it still plays a role in formatting messages with the relevant\ninformation to give the user a detailed message. Its purpose has shifted\nfrom printer to response generator.\n\nLet\u0027s make Ui\u0027s methods return the created string rather than print them\nto the command line.\n","fileTypesAndContributionMap":{"java":{"insertions":56,"deletions":63}}},{"hash":"39a2ae7a5e93c2820e5d59c0f94c9a924f6ff929","isMergeCommit":false,"messageTitle":"Refactor Ui class","messageBody":"","fileTypesAndContributionMap":{"java":{"insertions":16,"deletions":57}}},{"hash":"0bcba29290d8b84cbbd4e065c27e774be66d1c81","isMergeCommit":false,"messageTitle":"Refactor Bmo class","messageBody":"","fileTypesAndContributionMap":{"java":{"insertions":3,"deletions":18}}},{"hash":"d92945be3eb667add2cc82ed7c66ecef0605318f","isMergeCommit":false,"messageTitle":"Remove isExit property from Command","messageBody":"","fileTypesAndContributionMap":{"java":{"insertions":11,"deletions":17}}},{"hash":"77c20f9c7399af286022a0368dc79ad03dd8d8b7","isMergeCommit":false,"messageTitle":"Refactor Command classes","messageBody":"","fileTypesAndContributionMap":{"java":{"insertions":0,"deletions":3}}},{"hash":"82f78ceceef0e72d06fe72ef040640b84ce4f09e","isMergeCommit":false,"messageTitle":"Refactor utility classes","messageBody":"","fileTypesAndContributionMap":{"java":{"insertions":6,"deletions":12}}},{"hash":"17be400e2ff06a6d8f6921234e70b8135a0a8edf","isMergeCommit":false,"messageTitle":"Reduce indent in handleUserInput","messageBody":"","fileTypesAndContributionMap":{"java":{"insertions":15,"deletions":12}}},{"hash":"dc2f445b76c7066ae10f9cc06b88250913ae3739","isMergeCommit":false,"messageTitle":"Use Streams in TaskList","messageBody":"","fileTypesAndContributionMap":{"java":{"insertions":12,"deletions":16}}},{"hash":"0dd3a33e04adf2e5619dd222846bea188a9743ed","isMergeCommit":true,"messageTitle":"Merge pull request #2 from ram-nush/branch-A-Assertions to master","messageBody":"Add assertions in switch cases and Task creation","tags":["A-Assertions"],"fileTypesAndContributionMap":{}},{"hash":"52312b7139cf771452b0a1b2c240445b937f250d","isMergeCommit":true,"messageTitle":"Merge branch \u0027master\u0027 into branch-A-CodeQuality","messageBody":"","fileTypesAndContribut